    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>According to the botanical definition, fruit with a structure (the core) that clearly separates the seeds from the ovary tissue. Fruit that is characteristic of the pome is the apple. Small fruits commonly called "berries" are really pomes, such as the hawberries and juneberries.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
